feat(orchestrator): Implement agent and BPMN tools

This commit introduces a significant set of features to the orchestrator, including:

- A ReAct agent capable of interacting with the orchestrator through a set of tools.
- Tools for creating and managing worker agents.
- Tools for interacting with the Dgraph database.
- Tools for starting and managing BPMN processes.
- A RESTful API for interacting with the orchestrator.
- A flexible configuration system for managing AI models and other settings.